{"tid":2075093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE《Fanfare》短褲太緊身！子瑜下身形狀一覽無遺","createTime":"2020-06-22T15:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T13:48:49.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd87b0e5b65bcf691a4dc68121b00782d66adf9","tid":2075093,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZRNnoA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZRNnoA.png&h=f2197685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-06-22/900/20200622001846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-06-22%2F900%2F20200622001846.jpg&h=66c84c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE《Fanfare》短褲太緊身！子瑜下身形狀一覽無遺。（圖／YOUTUBE）<br />\n<br />\n南韓人氣女子天團TWICE，於6/19號發行全新日文單曲《Fanfare》並在官方YouTube頻道中推出MV，短短幾小時便衝上日本LINE MUSIC排行榜冠軍。而她們在MV中所穿水藍色海軍造型，也意外受到注意。<br />\n<br />\n6/1才發行全新韓文單曲《MORE &amp; MORE》的TWICE，19號再度發行日文全新單曲《Fanfare》，輕快的曲風加上色彩繽紛的風格，讓MV上線短短幾天便突破百萬點閱並成為下載音樂榜單上的第一名，人氣無法擋。<br />\n<br />\n這次除了旋律展現出TWICE的青春活力外，宮廷海軍風造型也令不少人印象深刻，眼尖的網友也發現這次的短褲造型十分貼身，將團員們的好身材完整呈現，又甜又性感令粉絲們招架不住，紛紛留言大讚「這次的造型真好看」、「她們無論韓文歌還是日文歌都好聽」、「子瑜這次鏡頭好多，被電暈」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-06-22/900/20200622001813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-06-22%2F900%2F20200622001813.jpg&h=64bf07b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE《Fanfare》短褲太緊身！子瑜「三角洲形狀」全都露（圖／YOUTUBE）<br />\n<br />\nIU私照流出下半身沒穿？坐下驚見「三角黑影」引暴動<br />\n「最狂小三」短褲直逼腿根！燦笑下半身白到發光<br />\nTWICE定延V領太低胸！彎腰「炸出黑影深溝」"},{"pid":"56b37276b782ec5b285fd2987c02446bd14fd3a2","tid":2075093,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"咁咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5